-- FRAME 10: evaluate validate-acyclicity (soft cell, LLM)
-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ
-- Ready set: { validate-acyclicity, spawn-sub-module-analyzers }
-- Pick: validate-acyclicity

вҠў validate-acyclicity
  given build-adjacencyвҶ’internal-edges вүЎ [("mayor","beads"), ("mayor","gt"), ("mayor","dolt"), ("witness","mayor"), ("witness","gt"), ("witness","dolt"), ("refinery","gt"), ("refinery","dolt"), ("beads","dolt"), ("gt","beads"), ("gt","dolt"), ("gt","refinery"), ("gt","mayor"), ("gt","witness")]
  given identify-modulesвҶ’modules вүЎ ["mayor", "witness", "refinery", "beads", "gt", "dolt"]
  yield is-acyclic, topological-order[], cycle-description

-- LLM evaluation:
-- Attempting topological sort on the internal dependency graph:
--   dolt: in-degree 0 (no deps) вҖ” candidate
--   Remove dolt вҶ’ beads in-degree drops to 0
--   Remove beads вҶ’ ...
--   But: mayor вҶ’ gt and gt вҶ’ mayor form a cycle.
--   Also: gt вҶ’ witness and witness вҶ’ mayor вҶ’ gt forms a longer cycle.
--
-- Cycle detected: gt вҶ’ mayor вҶ’ gt (direct cycle of length 2)
-- Additional cycle: gt вҶ’ witness вҶ’ mayor вҶ’ gt (length 3)

  yield is-acyclic вүЎ false

  yield topological-order вүЎ []

  yield cycle-description вүЎ "Two overlapping cycles detected. Cycle 1 (length 2): gt вҶ’ mayor вҶ’ gt. The gt CLI dispatches escalations to mayor, and mayor uses gt commands to communicate вҖ” creating a mutual dependency. Cycle 2 (length 3): gt вҶ’ witness вҶ’ mayor вҶ’ gt. The gt CLI triggers witness nudges, witness escalates to mayor, and mayor uses gt commands. Both cycles involve gt as the hub: gt orchestrates all modules, but several modules also invoke gt commands, creating circular dependencies."

-- oracle checks:
--   вҠЁ is-acyclic вҲҲ { true, false } вҶ’ вң“ (false)
--   вҠЁ if is-acyclic then topological-order contains all modules вҶ’ N/A (is-acyclic = false)
--   вҠЁ if not is-acyclic then cycle-description names the cycle вҶ’ вң“
--     (gt вҶ’ mayor вҶ’ gt named explicitly; gt вҶ’ witness вҶ’ mayor вҶ’ gt also named)

-- cell-level вҠЁ? on validate-acyclicity: retry max 2. Not triggered вҖ” oracles passed.

